<plot>A house is usually a place of refuge, a place of safety. People can't wait to get to the comfort of their home, or to hide from the outside world. Unfortunately for Alex, Sarah and Roger, the Emerson home is one house they will find themselves wanting to escape. IN THE DARK follows Alex, Sarah, and Roger as they find themselves trapped and tormented inside an otherwise-unassuming house. But could it be something else? Is what's happening even real? IN THE DARK puts aside hack-and-slash and pushes psychological horror in the tradition of classic horror movies.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?262952</url></doc>
